00:59:04.730 --> 00:59:05.140
and stuff.

00:59:05.990 --> 00:59:12.320
And we just want to make that easy because that is currently way too hard to make a Conda

00:59:12.220 --> 00:59:21.060
package is like a bunch of steps um and that also kind of precludes that you could use source and

00:59:21.110 --> 00:59:26.660
get dependencies for like other pixie projects because basically what we do what we will do in

00:59:26.660 --> 00:59:31.940
the background is like if you depend on a source dependency for another pixie project we will build

